view.name: Department of Motor Vehicle (DMV) Office Locations
view.description: This dataset contains the list of all Department of Motor Vehicle, (DMV), offices in NYS, with addresses, office hours, latitude and longitude coordinates, and phone numbers.

columns.name: Office Name
columns.description: The official DMV office name

columns.name: Office Type
Public Phone Number
columns.description: The office’s public phone number

columns.name: Public Phone Extension
columns.description: The office’s extension for public phone number if applicable

columns.name: Street Address Line 1
columns.description: The street name (first part) as assigned by a local governing authority for the office.

columns.name: Street Address Line 2
columns.description: The street name (second part) as assigned by a local governing authority for the office.

columns.name: City
columns.description: A valid city name for where the office resides.

columns.name: State
columns.description: The state where the office resides.

columns.name: Zip Code
columns.description: The code that identifies a specific geographic delivery area.

columns.name: Monday Beginning Hours
columns.description: The time (a.m.) the office opens on Mondays.

columns.name: Monday Ending Hours
columns.description: The time (p.m.) the office closes on Mondays.

columns.description: The time (a.m.) the office opens on Tuesdays.

columns.name: Tuesday Ending Hours
columns.description: The time (p.m.) the office closes on Tuesdays.

The time (a.m.) the office opens on

columns.description: Yes or no
